[
    {
        "content": "<p>If I have these inaccessible hypotheses, </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"bp\">✝</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∧</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n<span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"bp\">✝</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">α</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>is there a way to either use <code>apply</code> anonymously or <code>specialize</code> anonymously?</p>",
        "id": 467296015,
        "sender_full_name": "nrs",
        "timestamp": 1725378297
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>No, you are either supposed to name the hypotheses at the place where they were introduced (this is usually possible) or name them with <code>rename_i</code> or <code>next ... =&gt;</code></p>",
        "id": 467299040,
        "sender_full_name": "Kyle Miller",
        "timestamp": 1725378969
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>(Please give a <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mwe.html\">#mwe</a> for more specific advice)</p>",
        "id": 467299133,
        "sender_full_name": "Kyle Miller",
        "timestamp": 1725378989
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"306601\">Kyle Miller</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/113489-new-members/topic/Anonymous.20.60apply.60.20or.20.60specialize.60/near/467299040\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>No, you are either supposed to name the hypotheses at the place where they were introduced (this is usually possible) or name them with <code>rename_i</code> or <code>next ... =&gt;</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∧</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∧</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">cases</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">rename_i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">specialize</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">specialize</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">apply</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">And</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;;&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">assumption</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>For example, it seems to me natural in the above proof to abstract away this part:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">rename_i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">specialize</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">specialize</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>by directly specializing all possible statements</p>",
        "id": 467302723,
        "sender_full_name": "nrs",
        "timestamp": 1725379702
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>An example of using a tactic that can name the new hypotheses:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∧</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∧</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">obtain</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">specialize</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">specialize</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">apply</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">And</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;;&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">assumption</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 467303534,
        "sender_full_name": "Kyle Miller",
        "timestamp": 1725379884
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>This can be combined with <code>intro</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∧</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∧</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">specialize</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">specialize</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">apply</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">And</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;;&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">assumption</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 467303609,
        "sender_full_name": "Kyle Miller",
        "timestamp": 1725379909
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>(You can use <code>constructor</code> instead of <code>apply And.intro</code>. It does the same thing, but you don't need to know the name <code>And.intro</code>)</p>",
        "id": 467303784,
        "sender_full_name": "Kyle Miller",
        "timestamp": 1725379944
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"306601\">Kyle Miller</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/113489-new-members/topic/Anonymous.20.60apply.60.20or.20.60specialize.60/near/467303784\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>(You can use <code>constructor</code> instead of <code>apply And.intro</code>. It does the same thing, but you don't need to know the name <code>And.intro</code>)</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>ah very cool tips! thanks a lot, way sleeker looking</p>",
        "id": 467303879,
        "sender_full_name": "nrs",
        "timestamp": 1725379974
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I know this isn't directly the content of the question, but I wouldn't use <code>specialize</code> here, as I don't think it's contributing anything. Of course, you can golf this all the way down to:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">universe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">u</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">variable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">X</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">X</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Prop</span><span class=\"o\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∧</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∧</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">↦</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 467305272,
        "sender_full_name": "Jireh Loreaux",
        "timestamp": 1725380337
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Or, if you have allow a very small import:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Init</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">PropLemmas</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">universe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">u</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">variable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">X</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">X</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Prop</span><span class=\"o\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∧</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∧</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">forall_and</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">mpr</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 467305707,
        "sender_full_name": "Jireh Loreaux",
        "timestamp": 1725380439
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"197836\">Jireh Loreaux</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/113489-new-members/topic/Anonymous.20.60apply.60.20or.20.60specialize.60/near/467305272\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I know this isn't directly the content of the question, but I wouldn't use <code>specialize</code> here, as I don't think it's contributing anything. Of course, you can golf this all the way down to:</p>\n<p><div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">universe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">u</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">variable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">X</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">X</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Prop</span><span class=\"o\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∧</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∧</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">↦</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span>\n</code></pre></div><br>\n</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>woah! that is probably the most optimized version possible and nevertheless very clear in what it does. thanks!!</p>",
        "id": 467306417,
        "sender_full_name": "nrs",
        "timestamp": 1725380649
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>And of course, this is a basic logical tautology, so the <code>tauto</code> tactic works too <span aria-label=\"smile\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f642\" role=\"img\" title=\"smile\">:smile:</span></p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∧</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∧</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">tauto</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 467312761,
        "sender_full_name": "Kyle Miller",
        "timestamp": 1725382405
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I didn't remember that <code>tauto</code> handles <code>∀</code>. And in fact, it doesn't according to <code>#help tactic tauto</code>. <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"306601\">@Kyle Miller</span> what <em>exactly</em> is in scope for <code>tauto</code>?</p>",
        "id": 467321986,
        "sender_full_name": "Jireh Loreaux",
        "timestamp": 1725385019
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"197836\">@Jireh Loreaux</span> Oh, it seems that I've misunderstood the scope of tauto, and it accidentally works here.</p>\n<p>This is a tautology, but <code>tauto</code> fails for it:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∧</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">↔</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∧</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">tauto</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
